metadata.name: Leap of faith
metadata.description:
Leap of faith
I know this journey ain't easy.
It overwhelms me, when my closest kins pull me down. 
It aches when they attend to what would the world think, but me. 
It is frightening to walk all those scarcely lit path, without a consort. 
But I’m certain I’ll not close doors on my dreams today. 
For today, I choose to unwind my fairy wings
& travel that untrodden path. 
Call me arrogant! Call me selfish! 
But I shall not stop to rise above. 
For this is my leap of faith.
